Steps 
===================
1.Create Private repository on ECR.

2.Create IAM user with "adminstrator access " along with CLI access key and seurity key.

3. Goto AWS-CLI use below command 
$aws configure
aws access key - 
aws secret access key - 
region name - us-east-1
default format json - yes

4. In ECR go to repo, there is oprion "View Push Commands" 
$aws ecr get-login-password --region eu-north-1 | docker login --username AWS --password-stdin 084129280874.dkr.ecr.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com
$docker tag spring-demo:latest 084129280874.dkr.ecr.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/spring-demo:latest
$docker push 084129280874.dkr.ecr.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/spring-demo:latest




